paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the journey to diagnosis of wild-type transthyretin-mediated (ATTRwt) amyloidosis and compares it with hereditary ATTRv amyloidosis. However, no specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are mentioned in the text.

challenges: The paper did not mention any specific TTR gene variants.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the clinical journey and symptoms of ATTRwt and ATTRv amyloidosis without detailing specific genetic variants in the TTR gene.
